 The National President, Amalgamated Commercial Tricycle and Motorcycle Owners and Riders Association of Nigeria (ACOMORAN), Prince Adebayo Samsudeen Apelogun,  has described Buhari as a real leader and democract par excellence. He said the president had achieved successes in all sectors and “these have manifested in the lives of all Nigerians.” Apelogun made the remarks while addressing journalists on the activities of the association lined up to celebrate the first year of President Buhari’s second term in office.  He said Nigerian democracy had witnessed many problems,  but “our president’s intellectual capability, wisdom and vast experience in governance have largely contributed to its rapid development which is being commended by world leaders.” He urged the president to continue working assiduously for the progress of the country and prayed that Almighty Allah would give him   good health to lead Nigeria to the promised land.